<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV82">
<l>ettiṟattu mottuniṉṟu yarntuyarnta peṟṟiyōy</l>
<l>muttiṟattu mūrinīra rāvaṇaittu yiṉṟaniṉ</l>
<l>pattuṟutta cintaiyōṭu niṉṟupācam viṭṭavark</l>
<l>kettiṟattu miṉpamiṅku maṅkumeṅku mākumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You with a glory that is higher and higher, by [Your] being consistent in any state!</l>
<l>For those who have given up ties, remaining with the thoughts strongly impressed</l>
<l rend="indent">by [my] devotion for You,</l>
<l>who slept on the serpent-bed upon the ocean with the three types of waters,</l>
<l>All types of bliss will be possible here, there, and everywhere!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
